1. Take an egg or two and mix it around in a bowl.
2. Take a piece of bread and put it the bowl and cover it with the egg.
3. Take the bread out and put it in a pan for a little bit.
4. Flip when you feel it is lightly browned on the side.
5. Once the other side is done take it out of the pan and place it on a plate.
6. Top with toppings like syrup and whipped cream.
7. Enjoy!
